### Sign up
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "phone": "010-1234-5678"
}

### Sign in
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}